{
  "stem": "8679.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd like to recite them for you here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I recited them in German, and coming to Canada I never I had a script, but I wrote it down for my children and later grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In German it was-- [SPEAKING GERMAN] The English is, 'And if in the--' I better do it from here. 'And if in the distant future a Haman should rise again, bringing death and destruction to our people, then may the memory of this day give us hope and courage in our hours of danger.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And may we never lose the conviction that God will be always with us, as He was with us today.'",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do not think as a child I realized the impact, but it must have left an incredible mark on me, because when Hitler marched into Vienna, this poem all of a sudden-- it was many years later.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only 10 when I recited it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a young adult when Hitler came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remembered it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I don't know what power made me do to remember this poem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remembered it all through our years during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I passed it on to my children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I passed it on to my grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I visited a Jewish school in Vancouver, the Talmud Torah Academy, I passed it on to those children, as well as in Camp Hatikvah.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe the incredible belief in God was maybe also instrumental, that I came through it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There must be a higher power.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do not want to disappoint you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't celebrate Friday nights too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, uh, we continued going where we wanted to go, play in the park or whatever we did, even on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, uh, I always believed these are outward signs.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
